<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef7b9e57-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s100752"><num value="100752">§ 100752.</num><heading> Destruction of animals and plant life</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary may provide for the destruction of such animals and plant life as may be detrimental to the use of any System unit.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef7b9e58-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db">(<ref href="/us/pl/113/287/s3">Pub. L. 113–287, § 3</ref>, <date date="2014-12-19">Dec. 19, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/3111">128 Stat. 3111</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
